  "name": "Father's Bank Messenger Uniform",
  "description": "The uniform Father wears to his new job as a bank messenger. He refuses to take it off at home, sleeping in it despite the family's protests. The uniform transforms him from a defeated old man into a figure of rigid authority \u2014 it is both a symbol of the family's forced self-reliance and of Father's new identity as household enforcer. Its gold buttons grow increasingly tarnished, mirroring the family's slow decline.",
